

Things that should be done to the 3.0 release:


	1. remove all kow_config dependency in modules in favour of a kow_lib.json.object_type
		Status.URI_Parameters	=> Status.Request_Parameters/Attributes (figure out a cooler name)
	2. implement a method for retrieving specific configurations
		Get_Config( Component, Config := "setup" ); => ./components/[component]/data/[config].cfg
		Get_Config( Service, Config := "setup" );   => ./components/[component]/data/[service]_service.cfg
		Get_Config( Module, Config := "setup" );    => ./components/[component]/data/[module]_module.cfg

	* page service
	* menu module
	* security module
	* any other configurable module/service
	* module factories and get_name(module) should be refactored
	* look for and remove unused *.Util modules



The config (and resource) path should be default to:
	1 => ./data/
	2 => ./




